title: Biden tells Ukraine's Zelensky that US would respond 'swiftly and decisively' to any further Russian aggression - CNN
content:
1. Biden tells Ukraine's Zelensky that US would respond 'swiftly and decisively' to any further Russian aggression  CNN
  2. International Pressure Mounts On Putin To Not Invade Ukraine  CBS New York
  3. Biden speaks with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy  NPR
  4. Biden tells Zelenskyy U.S. will respond 'swiftly and decisively' if Russia invades Ukraine  Yahoo News
  5. Your Monday Briefing: Fears of Invasion Mount  The New York Times
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: President Joe Biden told Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky in a roughly hour-long call Sunday that the US would respond "swiftly and decisively" if Russia takes further steps toward invasion, according to a White House readout of the call.
